iwNeW","ref":"Ps.132.4","text":"I will not give sleep to mine eyes, or slumber to mine eyelids,"},{"id":"recaTEcPrmOe0OGss","ref":"Ps.132.5","text":"Until I find out a place for the LORD, an habitation for the mighty God of Jacob."},{"id":"recWxynYybtw09jYk","ref":"Ps.132.6","text":"Lo, we heard of it at Ephratah: we found it in the fields of the wood."},{"id":"recyrbZOC3ccS60fR","ref":"Ps.132.7","text":"We will go into his tabernacles: we will worship at his footstool."},{"id":"recfr7zkNgzfXHxk8","ref":"Ps.132.8","text":"Arise, O LORD, into thy rest; thou, and the ark of thy strength."}]}
